OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy start for England and
OL,6,FWales, with a few spots of rain or
OL,7,Fdrizzle. Brightening up from the east
OL,8,Fas the day progresses. Sunny spells
OL,9,Ffor Northern Ireland and Scotland. A
OL,10,Fnotably cooler day, with a chilly
OL,11,Fnortheasterly breeze.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FDry, with long clear periods
OL,14,Ffor most. Though generally cloudy
OL,15,Facross the northeast. Patchy frost and
OL,16,Ffog forming in the north, whilst the
OL,17,Fsouth will remain rather breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
