OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FMorning fog clearing to
OL,6,Fleave a sunny day for most. Perhaps a
OL,7,Ffew showers moving into the far
OL,8,Fsouthwest of England. Windy in the
OL,9,Fsouth. Feeling warm in the sunshine.
